      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for those who prioritize utility over perfection. While the car runs and drives fine, the exterior shows noticeable paint fading and several small dings consistent with its age. Inside, the upholstery has some minor staining and the electronics are mostly functional, though the radio display is occasionally temperamental. Mechanically, it is solid but will likely need a new set of tires and a routine brake service in the near future. It is a dependable workhorse that still has plenty of life left for a budget-conscious buyer.",
