      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive excellence, this vehicle has been curated to ensure both mechanical reliability and aesthetic integrity. Meticulously maintained and demonstrating a disciplined service history, it offers a refined driving experience that meets the rigorous standards of a discerning owner. This offering represents a superior balance of performance and value, prepared for immediate acquisition and long-term service.",
