      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for this absolute gem. It\u2019s been such a reliable ride and is still in wonderful shape, perfect for someone who wants a solid, well-cared-for car without the 'brand new' price tag. It\u2019s been a joy to own and is ready for many more adventures with its next owner. Come take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to love how it handles!",
